Package it.polimi.travlendarplus.RESTful.messages.calendarMessages.eventMessages

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddBreakEventMessage
    This is the message class sent in the body of an HTTP request to add a break event into the user's profile
    AddEventMessage
    This is the message class sent in the body of an HTTP request to add an event into the user's profile
    AddGenericEventMessage
    This is the message abstract class sent in the body of an HTTP request to add a generic event into the user's profile, it is to be extended by all event message classes
    BreakEventDescriptionResponse
    This is a message class sent to reply with all needed info to a breakEvent - related response
    ErrorListResponse
    This is a message class sent to reply to the client with a list of errors ( invalid fields or not satisfied conditions ) that are present in the request body
    EventDescriptionResponse
    This is a message class sent to reply with all needed info to a event - related response
    EventsListResponse
    This is a message class sent to reply with all needed info to a request that expects a list of event and breakEvents as reply
    LocationMessage
    Message used as a container of a location info.
    ModifyBreakEventMessage
    This is the message class sent in the body of an HTTP request to modify a breakEvent into the user's profile
    ModifyEventMessage
    This is the message class sent in the body of an HTTP request to modify an event into the user's profile
    PeriodMessage
    Message used as a container of a periodicity info.
